name: NFT NYC 2021
description:
I myself never made it to NFT NYC im an introvert i don't do big crowds of people. So instead i drew it as an urban watercolor. Different projects have made the billboards, from Apes, Punks, Longneck ladies by Nyla KidEight and his G'vol's , Foodmasku with his pizza on his face, KC and the Golden Poo, Sneakerheadz made it too. In the background those line pieces and Anonymous made it up there. 
Just having fun with creating.
